Interface RemoteObjFactory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Exporter, Importer
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface RemoteObjFactory
extends Importer, Exporter
    Interface that describes how to import and export RemoteObjs, that factories of RemoteObj must adhere to. They must implement export and import.
